{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":2048,"text":"I'm going to tell you a little bit\nabout my TEDxHouston Talk."},{"time":5841,"text":"I woke up the morning\nafter I gave that talk"},{"time":9404,"text":"with the worst vulnerability\nhangover of my life."},{"time":14346,"text":"And I actually didn't leave my house\nfor about three days."}]},{"cues":[{"time":20092,"text":"The first time I left\nwas to meet a friend for lunch."},{"time":23787,"text":"And when I walked in,\nshe was already at the table."},{"time":26233,"text":"I sat down, and she said,\n\"God, you look like hell.\""},{"time":29541,"text":"I said, \"Thanks. I feel really --"},{"time":32540,"text":"I'm not functioning.\""},{"time":34152,"text":"And she said, \"What's going on?\""},{"time":36350,"text":"And I said, \"I just told 500 people"},{"time":41967,"text":"that I became a researcher\nto avoid vulnerability."},{"time":45586,"text":"And that when being vulnerable\nemerged from my data,"},{"time":50066,"text":"as absolutely essential\nto whole-hearted living,"},{"time":54669,"text":"I told these 500 people\nthat I had a breakdown."},{"time":58716,"text":"I had a slide that said 'Breakdown.'"},{"time":60502,"text":"At what point did I think\nthat was a good idea?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":63000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":66145,"text":"And she said, \"I saw\nyour talk live-streamed."},{"time":68327,"text":"It was not really you."},{"time":70643,"text":"It was a little different\nthan what you usually do."},{"time":73049,"text":"But it was great.\""},{"time":74885,"text":"And I said,"},{"time":76401,"text":"\"This can't happen."},{"time":78000,"text":"YouTube, they're putting\nthis thing on YouTube."},{"time":80765,"text":"And we're going to be talking\nabout 600, 700 people.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":84936,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":88746,"text":"And she said,\n\"Well, I think it's too late.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":91897,"text":"And I said, \"Let me ask you something.\""},{"time":94201,"text":"And she said, \"Yeah.\""},{"time":95677,"text":"I said, \"Do you remember\nwhen we were in college,"},{"time":97994,"text":"really wild and kind of dumb?\""},{"time":100059,"text":"She said, \"Yeah.\""},{"time":101089,"text":"I said, \"Remember when\nwe'd leave a really bad message"},{"time":103739,"text":"on our ex-boyfriend's answering machine?"},{"time":106137,"text":"Then we'd have to break into his dorm room\nand then erase the tape?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":109769,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":112190,"text":"And she goes, \"Uh... no.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":114920,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":117154,"text":"Of course, the only thing\nI could say at that point was,"},{"time":119804,"text":"\"Yeah, me neither."},{"time":122133,"text":"Yeah -- me neither.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":124849,"text":"And I'm thinking to myself,"},{"time":128158,"text":"\"Bren√©, what are you doing?"},{"time":130000,"text":"Why did you bring this up?"},{"time":132249,"text":"Have you lost your mind?"},{"time":133874,"text":"Your sisters would be perfect for this.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":136183,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":137612,"text":"So I looked back up and she said,"},{"time":140766,"text":"\"Are you really going to try\nto break in and steal the video"},{"time":145544,"text":"before they put it on YouTube?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":147144,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":148656,"text":"And I said, \"I'm just thinking\nabout it a little bit.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":151640,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":153426,"text":"She said, \"You're like the worst\nvulnerability role model ever.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":158003,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":160937,"text":"Then I looked at her and I said something"},{"time":162929,"text":"that at the time felt a little dramatic,"},{"time":164881,"text":"but ended up being\nmore prophetic than dramatic."},{"time":168793,"text":"\"If 500 turns into 1,000"},{"time":172762,"text":"or 2,000,"},{"time":174246,"text":"my life is over.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":176594,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":178856,"text":"I had no contingency plan\nfor four million."}]},{"cues":[{"time":181341,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":185883,"text":"And my life did end when that happened."},{"time":188875,"text":"And maybe the hardest part\nabout my life ending"},{"time":192000,"text":"is that I learned something\nhard about myself,"},{"time":196971,"text":"and that was that,"},{"time":199439,"text":"as much as I would be frustrated"},{"time":201000,"text":"about not being able to get\nmy work out to the world,"},{"time":203548,"text":"there was a part of me\nthat was working very hard"},{"time":206000,"text":"to engineer staying small,"},{"time":209560,"text":"staying right under the radar."},{"time":213761,"text":"But I want to talk\nabout what I've learned."}]},{"cues":[{"time":215918,"text":"There's two things\nthat I've learned in the last year."},{"time":219287,"text":"The first is:"},{"time":222468,"text":"vulnerability is not weakness."},{"time":227295,"text":"And that myth is profoundly dangerous."},{"time":232283,"text":"Let me ask you honestly --"},{"time":234029,"text":"and I'll give you this warning,"},{"time":235861,"text":"I'm trained as a therapist,"},{"time":237171,"text":"so I can out-wait you uncomfortably --"},{"time":240000,"text":"so if you could just raise your hand\nthat would be awesome --"},{"time":243469,"text":"how many of you honestly,"},{"time":245000,"text":"when you're thinking about doing\nor saying something vulnerable"},{"time":248858,"text":"think, \"God, vulnerability is weakness.\""},{"time":251311,"text":"How many of you think of vulnerability\nand weakness synonymously?"},{"time":255319,"text":"The majority of people."},{"time":257136,"text":"Now let me ask you this question:"},{"time":258775,"text":"This past week at TED,"},{"time":261374,"text":"how many of you,\nwhen you saw vulnerability up here,"},{"time":264000,"text":"thought it was pure courage?"},{"time":268708,"text":"Vulnerability is not weakness."},{"time":271430,"text":"I define vulnerability as emotional risk,"},{"time":276234,"text":"exposure, uncertainty."},{"time":279425,"text":"It fuels our daily lives."},{"time":281611,"text":"And I've come to the belief --"},{"time":283183,"text":"this is my 12th year\ndoing this research --"},{"time":285452,"text":"that vulnerability is our most accurate\nmeasurement of courage --"},{"time":293929,"text":"to be vulnerable,\nto let ourselves be seen,"},{"time":296461,"text":"to be honest."}]},{"cues":[{"time":298663,"text":"One of the weird things that's happened\nis, after the TED explosion,"},{"time":302342,"text":"I got a lot of offers to speak\nall over the country --"},{"time":305999,"text":"everyone from schools and parent meetings"},{"time":308385,"text":"to Fortune 500 companies."},{"time":311000,"text":"And so many of the calls went like this,"},{"time":313441,"text":"\"Dr. Brown, we loved your TED talk."},{"time":315215,"text":"We'd like you to come in and speak."},{"time":317557,"text":"We'd appreciate it"},{"time":319000,"text":"if you wouldn't mention\nvulnerability or shame.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":321356,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":326739,"text":"What would you like for me to talk about?"},{"time":330089,"text":"There's three big answers."},{"time":331517,"text":"This is mostly, to be honest with you,\nfrom the business sector:"},{"time":334667,"text":"innovation, creativity and change."}]},{"cues":[{"time":338482,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":340514,"text":"So let me go on the record and say,"},{"time":344458,"text":"vulnerability is the birthplace\nof innovation, creativity and change."}]},{"cues":[{"time":349652,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":357855,"text":"To create is to make something\nthat has never existed before."},{"time":363704,"text":"There's nothing more vulnerable than that."},{"time":366681,"text":"Adaptability to change\nis all about vulnerability."}]},{"cues":[{"time":371466,"text":"The second thing,"},{"time":372579,"text":"in addition to really\nfinally understanding"},{"time":376409,"text":"the relationship between\nvulnerability and courage,"},{"time":378836,"text":"the second thing I learned, is this:"},{"time":381972,"text":"We have to talk about shame."},{"time":386285,"text":"And I'm going to be\nreally honest with you."},{"time":388817,"text":"When I became a \"vulnerability researcher\""},{"time":392365,"text":"and that became the focus\nbecause of the TED talk --"},{"time":395124,"text":"and I'm not kidding."}]},{"cues":[{"time":396920,"text":"I'll give you an example."},{"time":399132,"text":"About three months ago,\nI was in a sporting goods store"},{"time":402069,"text":"buying goggles and shin guards"},{"time":403522,"text":"and all the things that parents buy\nat the sporting goods store."},{"time":407121,"text":"About from a hundred feet away,\nthis is what I hear:"},{"time":409994,"text":"\"Vulnerability TED! Vulnerability TED!\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":412649,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":418545,"text":"(Laughter ends)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":419570,"text":"I'm a fifth-generation Texan."},{"time":422669,"text":"Our family motto is \"Lock and load.\""},{"time":425248,"text":"I am not a natural\nvulnerability researcher."},{"time":430430,"text":"So I'm like,"},{"time":432000,"text":"just keep walking, she's on my six."}]},{"cues":[{"time":434978,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":436422,"text":"And then I hear, \"Vulnerability TED!\""},{"time":440684,"text":"I turn around, I go, \"Hi.\""},{"time":443255,"text":"She's right here and she said,"},{"time":445909,"text":"\"You're the shame researcher\nwho had the breakdown.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":448719,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":452557,"text":"At this point, parents are, like,\npulling their children close."}]},{"cues":[{"time":457303,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":458428,"text":"\"Look away.\""},{"time":462612,"text":"And I'm so worn out\nat this point in my life,"},{"time":464992,"text":"I look at her and I actually say,"},{"time":466727,"text":"\"It was a fricking spiritual awakening.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":469385,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":471000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":473345,"text":"And she looks back and does this,"},{"time":476226,"text":"\"I know.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":477274,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":478299,"text":"And she said,"},{"time":480114,"text":"\"We watched your TED talk in my book club."},{"time":483116,"text":"Then we read your book\nand we renamed ourselves"},{"time":486489,"text":"'The Breakdown Babes.'\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":488490,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":489753,"text":"And she said, \"Our tagline is:"},{"time":491789,"text":"'We're falling apart\nand it feels fantastic.'\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":495000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":498853,"text":"You can only imagine what it's like\nfor me in a faculty meeting."}]},{"cues":[{"time":502925,"text":"(Sighs)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":505433,"text":"So when I became Vulnerability TED,"},{"time":508359,"text":"like an action figure --"},{"time":510922,"text":"Like Ninja Barbie,\nbut I'm Vulnerability TED --"},{"time":514938,"text":"I thought, I'm going to leave\nthat shame stuff behind,"},{"time":517641,"text":"because I spent six years studying shame"},{"time":520609,"text":"before I started writing\nand talking about vulnerability."},{"time":523474,"text":"And I thought, thank God,\nbecause shame is this horrible topic,"},{"time":526566,"text":"no one wants to talk about it."},{"time":528156,"text":"It's the best way to shut\npeople down on an airplane."},{"time":530658,"text":"\"What do you do?\" \"I study shame.\" \"Oh.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":532621,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":534868,"text":"And I see you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":536000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":542268,"text":"But in surviving this last year,"},{"time":546278,"text":"I was reminded of a cardinal rule --"},{"time":548953,"text":"not a research rule,"},{"time":551000,"text":"but a moral imperative\nfrom my upbringing --"},{"time":555249,"text":"\"you've got to dance\nwith the one who brung ya\"."},{"time":559329,"text":"And I did not learn about vulnerability"},{"time":561827,"text":"and courage and creativity and innovation"},{"time":564918,"text":"from studying vulnerability."},{"time":567744,"text":"I learned about these things\nfrom studying shame."},{"time":571532,"text":"And so I want to walk you in to shame."},{"time":575770,"text":"Jungian analysts call shame\nthe swampland of the soul."},{"time":581386,"text":"And we're going to walk in."},{"time":583100,"text":"And the purpose is not to walk in"},{"time":585000,"text":"and construct a home and live there."},{"time":588124,"text":"It is to put on some galoshes --"},{"time":591848,"text":"and walk through and find our way around."},{"time":597023,"text":"Here's why."}]},{"cues":[{"time":600387,"text":"We heard the most compelling call ever\nto have a conversation in this country,"},{"time":605617,"text":"and I think globally, around race, right?"},{"time":610184,"text":"Yes? We heard that."},{"time":611696,"text":"Yes?"},{"time":613347,"text":"Cannot have that conversation\nwithout shame."},{"time":616791,"text":"Because you cannot talk about race\nwithout talking about privilege."},{"time":620281,"text":"And when people start\ntalking about privilege,"},{"time":622448,"text":"they get paralyzed by shame."},{"time":624812,"text":"We heard a brilliant simple solution\nto not killing people in surgery,"},{"time":628986,"text":"which is, have a checklist."},{"time":631240,"text":"You can't fix that problem\nwithout addressing shame,"},{"time":634006,"text":"because when they teach\nthose folks how to suture,"},{"time":637000,"text":"they also teach them\nhow to stitch their self-worth"},{"time":640380,"text":"to being all-powerful."},{"time":642507,"text":"And all-powerful folks\ndon't need checklists."}]},{"cues":[{"time":647577,"text":"And I had to write down\nthe name of this TED Fellow"},{"time":649982,"text":"so I didn't mess it up here."},{"time":652212,"text":"Myshkin Ingawale,"},{"time":654045,"text":"I hope I did right by you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":655807,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":658919,"text":"I saw the TED Fellows my first day here."},{"time":660875,"text":"And he got up and he explained\nhow he was driven to create"},{"time":664265,"text":"some technology to help test for anemia,"},{"time":666463,"text":"because people were dying unnecessarily."},{"time":669408,"text":"And he said, \"I saw this need."},{"time":670929,"text":"So you know what I did? I made it.\""},{"time":672920,"text":"And everybody just burst into applause,\nand they were like \"Yes!\""},{"time":676199,"text":"And he said, \"And it didn't work."}]},{"cues":[{"time":677918,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":679071,"text":"And then I made it 32 more times,"},{"time":682826,"text":"and then it worked.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":684715,"text":"You know what the big secret about TED is?"},{"time":687033,"text":"I can't wait to tell people this."},{"time":688630,"text":"I guess I'm doing it right now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":690348,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":692476,"text":"This is like the failure conference."}]},{"cues":[{"time":694523,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":695801,"text":"No, it is."}]},{"cues":[{"time":696970,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":699753,"text":"You know why this place is amazing?"},{"time":702978,"text":"Because very few people here\nare afraid to fail."},{"time":707185,"text":"And no one who gets on the stage,\nso far that I've seen, has not failed."},{"time":710927,"text":"I've failed miserably, many times."},{"time":713768,"text":"I don't think the world understands that,"},{"time":716379,"text":"because of shame."}]},{"cues":[{"time":718718,"text":"There's a great quote\nthat saved me this past year"},{"time":721101,"text":"by Theodore Roosevelt."},{"time":722518,"text":"A lot of people refer to it\nas the \"Man in the Arena\" quote."},{"time":726604,"text":"And it goes like this:"},{"time":728000,"text":"\"It is not the critic who counts."},{"time":730835,"text":"It is not the man who sits and points out"},{"time":733430,"text":"how the doer of deeds\ncould have done things better"},{"time":735933,"text":"and how he falls and stumbles."},{"time":737948,"text":"The credit goes to the man in the arena"},{"time":741039,"text":"whose face is marred\nwith dust and blood and sweat."},{"time":745888,"text":"But when he's in the arena,"},{"time":749300,"text":"at best, he wins,"},{"time":751490,"text":"and at worst, he loses,"},{"time":753374,"text":"but when he fails, when he loses,"},{"time":755643,"text":"he does so daring greatly.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":759228,"text":"And that's what this conference,\nto me, is about."},{"time":761873,"text":"Life is about daring greatly,\nabout being in the arena."},{"time":765460,"text":"When you walk up to that arena\nand you put your hand on the door,"},{"time":768533,"text":"and you think, \"I'm going in\nand I'm going to try this,\""},{"time":771208,"text":"shame is the gremlin"},{"time":772607,"text":"who says, \"Uh, uh."},{"time":774853,"text":"You're not good enough."},{"time":776583,"text":"You never finished that MBA.\nYour wife left you."},{"time":779948,"text":"I know your dad really\nwasn't in Luxembourg,"},{"time":782020,"text":"he was in Sing Sing."},{"time":785461,"text":"I know those things\nthat happened to you growing up."},{"time":788986,"text":"I know you don't think"},{"time":790471,"text":"that you're pretty, smart,\ntalented or powerful enough."},{"time":793352,"text":"I know your dad never paid attention,\neven when you made CFO.\""},{"time":797884,"text":"Shame is that thing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":800417,"text":"And if we can quiet it down and walk in"},{"time":803861,"text":"and say, \"I'm going to do this,\""},{"time":807449,"text":"we look up and the critic\nthat we see pointing and laughing,"},{"time":811000,"text":"99 percent of the time is who?"},{"time":814635,"text":"Us."},{"time":817302,"text":"Shame drives two big tapes --"},{"time":819000,"text":"\"never good enough\" --"},{"time":821846,"text":"and, if you can talk it out of that one,"},{"time":823973,"text":"\"who do you think you are?\""},{"time":827339,"text":"The thing to understand\nabout shame is, it's not guilt."},{"time":830147,"text":"Shame is a focus on self,\nguilt is a focus on behavior."},{"time":832982,"text":"Shame is \"I am bad.\""},{"time":834687,"text":"Guilt is \"I did something bad.\""},{"time":837767,"text":"How many of you,"},{"time":839000,"text":"if you did something\nthat was hurtful to me,"},{"time":841259,"text":"would be willing to say,\n\"I'm sorry. I made a mistake?\""},{"time":844124,"text":"How many of you would be\nwilling to say that?"},{"time":846641,"text":"Guilt: I'm sorry. I made a mistake."},{"time":849387,"text":"Shame: I'm sorry. I am a mistake."}]},{"cues":[{"time":853387,"text":"There's a huge difference\nbetween shame and guilt."},{"time":855974,"text":"And here's what you need to know."},{"time":857966,"text":"Shame is highly, highly correlated"},{"time":860434,"text":"with addiction, depression,\nviolence, aggression,"},{"time":863685,"text":"bullying, suicide, eating disorders."},{"time":867375,"text":"And here's what you even\nneed to know more."},{"time":869604,"text":"Guilt, inversely correlated\nwith those things."},{"time":874623,"text":"The ability to hold something\nwe've done or failed to do"},{"time":878083,"text":"up against who we want to be\nis incredibly adaptive."},{"time":881495,"text":"It's uncomfortable, but it's adaptive."}]},{"cues":[{"time":887499,"text":"The other thing you need\nto know about shame"},{"time":889571,"text":"is it's absolutely organized by gender."},{"time":893214,"text":"If shame washes over me\nand washes over Chris,"},{"time":896060,"text":"it's going to feel the same."},{"time":898338,"text":"Everyone sitting in here knows\nthe warm wash of shame."},{"time":901553,"text":"We're pretty sure that the only people\nwho don't experience shame"},{"time":904625,"text":"are people who have no capacity\nfor connection or empathy."},{"time":908125,"text":"Which means, yes, I have a little shame;"},{"time":910054,"text":"no, I'm a sociopath."},{"time":911570,"text":"So I would opt for, yes,\nyou have a little shame."},{"time":917574,"text":"Shame feels the same for men and women,"},{"time":919613,"text":"but it's organized by gender."}]},{"cues":[{"time":922105,"text":"For women,"},{"time":924200,"text":"the best example I can give you\nis Enjoli, the commercial."},{"time":929910,"text":"\"I can put the wash on the line,\npack the lunches, hand out the kisses"},{"time":933220,"text":"and be at work at five to nine."},{"time":936037,"text":"I can bring home the bacon,\nfry it up in the pan"},{"time":938373,"text":"and never let you forget you're a man.\""},{"time":941483,"text":"For women, shame is, do it all,"},{"time":943995,"text":"do it perfectly"},{"time":945111,"text":"and never let them see you sweat."},{"time":948504,"text":"I don't know how much perfume\nthat commercial sold,"},{"time":951000,"text":"but I guarantee you,"},{"time":952680,"text":"it moved a lot of antidepressants\nand anti-anxiety meds."}]},{"cues":[{"time":955691,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":959654,"text":"Shame, for women, is this web"},{"time":962376,"text":"of unobtainable, conflicting,\ncompeting expectations"},{"time":966268,"text":"about who we're supposed to be."},{"time":969506,"text":"And it's a straight-jacket."}]},{"cues":[{"time":971784,"text":"For men,"},{"time":973000,"text":"shame is not a bunch of competing,\nconflicting expectations."},{"time":976449,"text":"Shame is one,"},{"time":978158,"text":"do not be perceived as what?"},{"time":981213,"text":"Weak."},{"time":983168,"text":"I did not interview men\nfor the first four years of my study."},{"time":986442,"text":"It wasn't until a man looked at me\nafter a book signing, and said,"},{"time":989724,"text":"\"I love what say about shame,"},{"time":991276,"text":"I'm curious why you didn't mention men.\""},{"time":993253,"text":"And I said, \"I don't study men.\""},{"time":995258,"text":"And he said, \"That's convenient.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":998313,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1001304,"text":"And I said, \"Why?\""},{"time":1002471,"text":"And he said, \"Because\nyou say to reach out,"},{"time":1005326,"text":"tell our story,"},{"time":1007717,"text":"be vulnerable."},{"time":1010278,"text":"But you see those books you just signed\nfor my wife and my three daughters?\""},{"time":1015139,"text":"I said, \"Yeah.\""},{"time":1017084,"text":"\"They'd rather me die\non top of my white horse"},{"time":1019305,"text":"than watch me fall down."},{"time":1023235,"text":"When we reach out and be vulnerable,"},{"time":1025000,"text":"we get the shit beat out of us."},{"time":1028290,"text":"And don't tell me"},{"time":1029632,"text":"it's from the guys\nand the coaches and the dads."},{"time":1034033,"text":"Because the women in my life\nare harder on me than anyone else.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":1038360,"text":"So I started interviewing men\nand asking questions."},{"time":1041864,"text":"And what I learned is this:"},{"time":1044566,"text":"You show me a woman\nwho can actually sit with a man"},{"time":1046971,"text":"in real vulnerability and fear,"},{"time":1049031,"text":"I'll show you a woman\nwho's done incredible work."},{"time":1052388,"text":"You show me a man who can sit with a woman"},{"time":1054873,"text":"who's just had it,"},{"time":1056680,"text":"she can't do it all anymore,"},{"time":1060156,"text":"and his first response is not,"},{"time":1062029,"text":"\"I unloaded the dishwasher!\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":1064497,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1065536,"text":"But he really listens --"},{"time":1067521,"text":"because that's all we need --"},{"time":1069000,"text":"I'll show you a guy\nwho's done a lot of work."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1072006,"text":"Shame is an epidemic in our culture."},{"time":1076696,"text":"And to get out from underneath it --"},{"time":1081440,"text":"to find our way back to each other,"},{"time":1083797,"text":"we have to understand how it affects us"},{"time":1085702,"text":"and how it affects\nthe way we're parenting,"},{"time":1088429,"text":"the way we're working,\nthe way we're looking at each other."},{"time":1092851,"text":"Very quickly, some research\nby Mahalik at Boston College."},{"time":1096279,"text":"He asked, what do women need to do\nto conform to female norms?"},{"time":1099624,"text":"The top answers in this country:"},{"time":1103532,"text":"nice, thin, modest"},{"time":1105000,"text":"and use all available\nresources for appearance."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1107266,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1109083,"text":"When he asked about men,"},{"time":1110420,"text":"what do men in this country need to do\nto conform with male norms,"},{"time":1114872,"text":"the answers were:"},{"time":1116453,"text":"always show emotional control,"},{"time":1118493,"text":"work is first,"},{"time":1120071,"text":"pursue status and violence."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1123420,"text":"If we're going to find\nour way back to each other,"},{"time":1125877,"text":"we have to understand and know empathy,"},{"time":1128000,"text":"because empathy's the antidote to shame."},{"time":1130619,"text":"If you put shame in a Petri dish,"},{"time":1132936,"text":"it needs three things\nto grow exponentially:"},{"time":1135269,"text":"secrecy, silence and judgment."},{"time":1137661,"text":"If you put the same amount in a Petri dish\nand douse it with empathy,"},{"time":1140939,"text":"it can't survive."},{"time":1142343,"text":"The two most powerful words\nwhen we're in struggle:"},{"time":1145675,"text":"me too."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1147707,"text":"And so I'll leave you with this thought."},{"time":1151008,"text":"If we're going to find our way\nback to each other,"},{"time":1155414,"text":"vulnerability is going to be that path."},{"time":1159401,"text":"And I know it's seductive\nto stand outside the arena,"},{"time":1161938,"text":"because I think I did it my whole life,"},{"time":1163823,"text":"and think to myself,"},{"time":1165100,"text":"I'm going to go in there and kick some ass"},{"time":1167587,"text":"when I'm bulletproof and when I'm perfect."},{"time":1172102,"text":"And that is seductive."},{"time":1173436,"text":"But the truth is, that never happens."},{"time":1176859,"text":"And even if you got\nas perfect as you could"},{"time":1179041,"text":"and as bulletproof as you\ncould possibly muster"},{"time":1181653,"text":"when you got in there,"},{"time":1182772,"text":"that's not what we want to see."},{"time":1186743,"text":"We want you to go in."},{"time":1189743,"text":"We want to be with you\nand across from you."},{"time":1193116,"text":"And we just want,"},{"time":1194832,"text":"for ourselves and the people we care about"},{"time":1197232,"text":"and the people we work with,"},{"time":1199082,"text":"to dare greatly."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1200463,"text":"So thank you all very much.\nI really appreciate it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1203000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}